*stupid programs for beginner to setup/reset & add new wifi network in linux terminal*
//compile those programs by commands

pi@raspberrypi:~$cc -o yourfavouritename(setup) stupid-linux-cmd-wifi-setup.c
pi@raspberrypi:~$cc -o yourfavouritename(add) add-new-wifi-linux-cmd.c

//execute those programs by commands

pi@raspberrypi:~$sudo ./yourfavouritename(setup) yourwifiname password
pi@raspberrypi:~$sudo ./yourfavouritename(add) yourwifiname password